<DL>
 <DT>Syntax:
 <DD><CODE>Repeat</CODE> <VAR>tactic</VAR>
 <DT>Effect:
 <DD>Repeats <VAR>tactic</VAR> as often as possible, but with a
               maximum of 10 times. So it is ensured the repetition
               always ends.
 <DT>See also:
 <DD><A HREF="#Try"><CODE>Try</CODE></A>,
     <A HREF="#Then"><CODE>Then</CODE></A>
</DL>
